flowchart LR
    C[Client] --> API[Shared API]
    API --> CTX[Signed Tenant Context]
    CTX --> DAL[Tenant-Scoped Data Access Layer]
    DAL --> DB[(Shared DB + RLS)]
    API --> CACHE[(Tenant-Namespaced Cache)]
    API --> Q[(Tenant-Scoped Queue)]
    Q --> W[Worker with Context Validation]
    W --> DB

    NOTE1[All reads/writes require tenant scope]
    NOTE2[Cache and queue payloads include tenant namespace]

    DAL -.-> NOTE1
    CACHE -.-> NOTE2
